snippet.title: Charles Dickens Quotes #shorts
snippet.description:
Charles Dickens Quotes #shorts

Charles John Huffam Dickens FRSA was an English writer and social critic. He created some of the world's best-known fictional characters and is regarded by many as the greatest novelist of the Victorian era.

These are vivid sayings and quotes from Charles Dickens. The best quotes and aphorisms of Charles Dickens that will make you think about many things in life. Life quotes from Charles Dickens are definitely worth your time.

Thank you for watching!
